column2: select s.ra, s.dec, x.ids, s.bestobjid, s.specobjid, galspec.h_beta_flux, galspec.oiii_#_flux, galspec.h_alpha_flux, galspec.nii_#_flux into mydb.xrayagn_bptlines from specobjall as s inner join mydb.xrayagn_ids as x on x.ids = s.bestobjid inner join galspecline as galspec on galspec.specobjid = s.specobjid order by s.ra ASC;
